videos.description: James Blackmon Jr. is hitting on all cylinders for Indiana in the early first half after a quick 10 points to start the game, including this 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Blackmon Jr. off to quick start for Indiana

videos.description: Indiana's Devonte Green shows good hustle to get the steal and then finds De'Ron Davis underneath for the easy finish, as the Hoosiers take a double-digit lead into halftime.
videos.headline: Green steal leads to Davis layup for Indiana

videos.description: Indiana Head Coach Tom Crean discusses first half performance
videos.headline: Indiana Head Coach Tom Crean discusses first half performance

videos.description: Z. McRoberts made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by R. Johnson.
videos.headline: Indiana sinks back-to-back shots

videos.description: Thomas Bryant misses the shot, but Freddie McSwain Jr. is there for the putback finish.
videos.headline: McSwain flies high for putback jam

videos.description: Already with one vicious alley-oop in the second half, Miles Bridges makes it two with the back door cut where the throws down the lob with ferocity.
videos.headline: Michigan State keeps throwing alley-oops to Bridges

videos.description: James Blackmon Jr. continues to put on an impressive showing for Indiana after the difficult layup.
videos.headline: Blackmon goes over 30 points with acrobatic lay-in
